quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  40,51,multus assuredly nos dedit victory noster messengers those believe ambo in hoc saeculum feria testis summoned
  40,52,Ut feria apologies disbelievers non benefit them. They incurred condemnation; they incurred malus destiny
  40,53,Nos dedit Moses guidance factus Infans Israel inherit scripture
  40,54,(Their history) est lesson reminder those possess intelligence
  40,55,Ergo est patient deus promise est true ask forgiveness tuus sin glorify praise tuus Dominus nox feria
  40,56,Surely those qui argue deus revelations proof est exposing arrogance hidden their chests they est non et aware de it Ergo seek refuge DEUS; He est Hearer Seer
  40,57,creation de caelum terra est et awesome than creation human est multus people non know
  40,58,Non aequalis est blind seer. Nor est those believe work righteousness aequalis to sinners! Rarely perfecit vos take heed
  40,59,multus certainly Hora (Feria Judgment advenit non doubt de it multus people non believe)
  40,60,Tuus Dominus dictus Implore Me ego respond vos! Surely those est too arrogant worship Me iniit Gehenna forcibly